{"tid":1375961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"灰心嘅人請入黎","createTime":"2019-07-28T07:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T08:14:23.000Z","uid":185387,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69021b14e3c77eab5cf815ba28fd01168ff40c5e","tid":1375961,"uid":185387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W4EdU7fPnA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW4EdU7fPnA8&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=0c2e88be\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W4EdU7fPnA8</a><br />\n<br />\n再聽一次，再問自己 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你愛唔愛香港？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你話你愛你男/女朋友，但唔同去行街拍拖，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">淨係識屌，係唔係愛？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n愛，係要行動同付出，唔係責罵。<br />\n<br />\n互屌係唔會令一段關係長久，同樣唯有<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">持續嘅愛同行動先可以令運動長久！！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">728 請出黎</span></span></strong></strong>，同所有人講你依然好愛香港"},{"pid":"d050abef7d5294d81fe5159615407b5e6e5f9d5d","tid":1375961,"uid":185387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"d51579ed2e441488567d1b89c6ac44aa1c89702d","tid":1375961,"uid":185387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"15e602556191c962fa228da324d1d558ea4e4217","tid":1375961,"uid":185387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:55:23.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"e0be8ec09a13bb5d99bd011304e78b3a96cbe674","tid":1375961,"uid":185387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"07ff701774516da8385adf4190946ca248ce62a6","tid":1375961,"uid":281720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited